-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

SELECT file_date, country, confirmed , deaths, covid_lookup.population, deaths/confirmed/1.0 as "Mortality_ratio"  from covid19 , covid_lookup 
where covid19.country  = covid_lookup.country_region 
and covid19.country IN ('Greece', 'Italy', 'Spain', 'United Kingdom', 'Portugal', 'Germany', 'Netherlands', 'Sweden')

-- Note: Unless you save your query, these tabs will NOT persist if you clear your cookies or change browsers.

select concat('US-', abbr) as code, state, iso2, iso3, deaths , confirmed , recovered , country , province , covid19.admin2, latitude , longitude, population ,file_date  
from covid_lookup, covid19
, state_abbreviation abbrvs

where 
covid_lookup.province_state = covid19.province
AND country_region = 'US'
and
country = 'United States'
and abbrvs.state = covid19.province
